        "TileImage": "$($repository b93a2ccd-8a06-4ecf-a5e6-296a49d274f5).Image",
        "Description": "Sean Rose has hired Chef Robert Powell to feed Colorado&apos;s hungriest soldiers. What kind of chef is packing a rifle at all times? Well, the kind of chef who knows how to get away with murder - via poisonous meatballs - yum! Which is exactly why Rose hired him. Now that Powell has taken out multiple suspicious personnal, his employment has run its course. Along with him, Larry, Miguel and Penelope,who all took part in this charade. Let&apos;s hope our contract with Rose can end on friendlier terms, 47.",
